<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.2.6">
<l>vaṭavarai niṉṟumvan tiṉṟuka ṇapuram</l>
<l>iṭavakai koḷvatu yāmeṉṟu pēciṉāḷ</l>
<l>maṭavaral mātareṉ pētai yivarkkivaḷ</l>
<l>kaṭavateṉ kaṇṭuyi liṉṟivar koḷḷavē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“Coming from the northern mountain,</l>
<l>Today we take up house in Kaṇṇapuram,” she says.</l>
<l>The naïve lady, this woman, my simple girl</l>
<l>What is her duty to him since he robs her sleep now?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
